-------------------------------------------------------------------
 Custom commands for running FRESCO Client on cluster
-------------------------------------------------------------------
If you need to look inside them, go to /home/<username>/fresco/bin.

 startclient
    A script that calls FrescoClient as a daemon with the IP address 
    specified inside the startclient script.  

 stopclient
    Terminates all FrescoClient processes with the kill command.

 FrescoClient
    You can run FrescoClient directly, much like using 'startclient'.

